## Performance
- Use `loading.tsx` for Suspense boundaries
- Use `dynamic` import for heavy client components
- Optimize images with `next/image`
- Use `fetchCache` and `revalidate` for caching strategies

## Security
- Validate all inputs with Zod on the server
- Check auth + role in every Server Action and page
- Never expose internal IDs in URLs where avoidable вЂ” use slugs
- Sanitize Markdown/HTML content before rendering
